posting_body: ['101 Grant Street managed by Cornerstone Apartments', 'Bedrooms:', '0', 'Bathrooms:', '1', 'Square Ft.:', '390', 'Price:', '$1345/mo.', 'Welcome to The Vista at Washington Park, a high rise building overlooking the beautiful neighborhood of Wash Park.', 'With a media room, fitness center, business center, and amazon lockers, this place has plenty of amenities for all of your needs!', "Located in a beautiful neighborhood of houses, you'll find dog walkers, joggers, and any assortment of active people.", 'On the weekends, take a trip to the fun Cherry Creek shopping center, a famous denver mall with a variety of stores to browse at your leisure.', 'Come visit The Vista at Washington Park today!', 'Features:', 'Media Room', 'Communal Kitchen', 'Community Grill', 'Coffee Machine', 'Recycling', 'Off-Street Parking', 'Elevator', 'Storage', 'Rooftop Deck', 'Vinyl Plank Floors', 'On-Site Coinless Laundry', 'Lounge Area', 'Contact us:', 'To schedule a showing please contact our leasing team at', 'To apply NOW please visit <URL>', 'Nearby Neighborhoods:', "Congress Park, Sloan's Lake, Five Points, Downtown, Baker, Jefferson Park, Uptown, Cheesman Park, RiNo, West Wash Park, Hale, Highlands, City Park, Platt Park, University of Denver, Capitol Hill, LoHi", 'Availability and pricing are subject to change.']
